      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk, that just feels like something people say because they're uncomfortable with the truth. it's just empty platitudes. if i actually vanished, the world wouldn't even stutter. it's not even sad when i think about it anymore, it's almost... peaceful. just the idea of finally being able to stop trying so hard and just fade out.",
